        "subject": "LU-00000: Test patch",
        "message": "LU-00000: Test patch\n\nBisect shows that this patch passes the test case.\nLocal testing indeed shows it is passing and without\nit the there is failure / intermittent failures.\nThis patch is based on LU-17871 by Andriy. It could\nnot cleanly applied without getting all the other\nldlm (interval tree) bits. This is a test patch to\nverify it passes maloo.\n\nOriginal patch:\nLU-17871 ldlm: FLOCK ownlocks may be not set\n\nConflict checking loop should continue until ownlocks is set.\nOwnlocks variable is essential for lock merges.\n\nSigned-off-by: Arshad Hussain <arshad.hussain@aeoncomputing.com>\nChange-Id: I8d3b421c57a00a9e2685f9216cc1844b01f9b70c\n"
